          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今有善门福地，荫功浩大，德行无边，我等奉玉帝敕旨前往赐宝降祥。列位大"
        },
        {
          "character": "天喜星",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等也为此事而来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "水官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此一同前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四仙官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "已到福地。"
        },
        {
          "character": "水官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙哇。但见炉烟结彩，瑞霭缤纷，时逢美景，欣遇良辰。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "水官",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "地灵产瑞草，"
        },
        {
          "character": "四仙官",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天相吉人家。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同挂玉钩） 早则见善门福地喜非常，"
        },
        {
          "character": "水官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位大仙各将吉言献上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "八如意",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领法旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "天福星",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "福堂霭霭瑞云生，"
        },
        {
          "character": "天禄星",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禄坐千钟享万灵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "天寿星",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寿同山岳添筹算，"
        },
        {
          "character": "天财星",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "财源广聚库填盈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "天喜星",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喜从天降重重至，"
        },
        {
          "character": "八如意",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "八节康宁事事成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "水官",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兰孙桂子多荣耀，"
        },
        {
          "character": "四仙官",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "满门欢乐贺升平。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同梅花酒） 献蟠桃，帝露扬，"
        },
        {
          "character": "四仙官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "庆贺已毕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "水官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列为大仙各归洞府。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四仙官",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领法旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同清江引） 赏心乐事如天上，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
